	<h1 class="title">为什么说华尔街从业者“叛逃”去硅谷是件好事儿？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Neil Irwin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-27 08:20:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7804/medium/7804.jpg?1436693707" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


